# Volkovo, Dmitriyevsky Selsoviet, Ufimsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan

}}
Volkovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Dmitriyevsky Selsoviet, Ufimsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 707 as of 2010.
Geography
It is located 33&nbsp;km from Ufa, 20&nbsp;km from Dmitriyevka.
